code: @Test public void validateCache() {     Cache countries = this.cacheManager.getCache("countries").     assertThat(countries).isNotNull().     // Simple test assuming the cache is empty     countries.clear().     assertThat(countries.get("BE")).isNull().     Country be = this.countryRepository.findByCode("BE").     assertThat((Country) countries.get("BE").get()).isEqualTo(be). }
